IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User MAILUSER
PassCmd "pass show web/posteo | sed -n 1p"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.mail/posteo/Inbox/
MapInbox Inbox
Flatten .

Channel posteo
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Patterns * !Inbox
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
User MAILUSER
PassCmd "pass show web/mailbox | sed -n 1p"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

MaildirStore mailbox-local
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/abn/
Inbox ~/.mail/abn/Inbox/
MapInbox Inbox
Flatten .

Channel mailbox
Master :mailbox-remote:
Slave :mailbox-local:
Patterns * !Inbox
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
